Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:15.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,心脏停止液注入完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:16.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:17.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起！
